'''布伊格林公馆'''（Hôtel de Boisgelin）是[[普罗旺斯地区艾克斯|普罗旺斯地区艾克斯]]的一座历史建筑，位于[[马扎然区|马扎然区]]（Quartier Mazarin）的九月四日街（rue du Quatre Septembre）11号，在[[四海豚广场|四海豚广场]]（Place des Quatre Dauphins） <ref name="tourism">{{Cite web |url=http://www.aixenprovencetourism.com/aix-hp-mazarin.htm |title=Aix-en-Provence Tourism: Hôtels particuliers |access-date=2013-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203125313/http://www.aixenprovencetourism.com/aix-hp-mazarin.htm |archive-date=2013-12-03 }}</ref><ref name="provence2009">''Provence'', Le Petit Futé, 2009 p. 169[https://books.google.com/books?id=v8wvE2FRbzoC&pg=PA169&dq=%22h%C3%B4tel+de+boisgelin%22+aix&hl=en&sa=X&ei=Whe6UunwBfHn7AbyoICgAQ&ved=0CDgQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=%22h%C3%B4tel%20de%20boisgelin%22%20aix&f=false]</ref><ref>Douglas Goldring, ''The South of France: The Lower Rhône Valley and the Mediterranean Seaboard from Martigues to Menton'', Macdonald, 1952, p. 116 [https://books.google.com/books?id=ze8aAAAAMAAJ&q=%22H%C3%B4tel+de+Boisgelin%22+aix&dq=%22H%C3%B4tel+de+Boisgelin%22+aix&hl=en&sa=X&ei=OWe7UszVIOTT7AbIu4DIAQ&ved=0CGcQ6AEwBTgU]</ref>

==历史==
它是由建筑师皮埃尔·帕维永（Pierre Pavillon，1612-1670）和让·克劳德·拉姆伯特（Jean-Claude Rambot，1621-1694）设计，为路易·勒·布兰科·蒙特斯邦建于1650年。<ref name="tourism"/><ref name="rene">René Borricand, ''Les Hôtels particuliers d'Aix-en-Provence'', 39 rue Espariat, 1971, p. 45 [https://books.google.com/books?id=_NYfAAAAMAAJ&q=%22H%C3%B4tel+de+Boisgelin%22+aix&dq=%22H%C3%B4tel+de+Boisgelin%22+aix&hl=en&sa=X&ei=OWe7UszVIOTT7AbIu4DIAQ&ved=0CFoQ6AEwAzgU] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=_NYfAAAAMAAJ&q=%22H%C3%B4tel+de+Boisgelin%22+aix&dq=%22H%C3%B4tel+de+Boisgelin%22+aix&hl=en&sa=X&ei=OWe7UszVIOTT7AbIu4DIAQ&ved=0CFoQ6AEwAzgU |date=20181215022554 }}</ref><ref>''Histoire d'Aix-en-Provence'', C.Y. Chaudoreille, 1977, p. 174 [https://books.google.com/books?id=WAx4AAAAIAAJ&q=%22H%C3%B4tel+de+Boisgelin%22+aix&dq=%22H%C3%B4tel+de+Boisgelin%22+aix&hl=en&sa=X&ei=OWe7UszVIOTT7AbIu4DIAQ&ved=0CGEQ6AEwBDgU]</ref> 1697年，皮埃尔·约瑟夫·劳伦斯·布鲁<ref name="rene"/> 购买了该建筑。那年，他委托建筑师劳伦·瓦隆(1652-1724) 设计了室内的大楼梯<ref name="tourism"/>。后来传给布伊格林家族<ref name="tourism"/>。 

它带有庭院和花园。<ref name="rene"/>在花园中，枝叶下有一个喷泉，因此白天总是在阴凉处<ref>Henri Dobler, ''Le cadre de la vie mondaine à Aix-en-Provence aux XVIIe et XVIIIe siècles: Boudoirs et jardins'', F. Detaille, 1928, p. 119 [https://books.google.com/books?id=sGZJAQAAIAAJ&q=%22H%C3%B4tel+de+Boisgelin%22+aix&dq=%22H%C3%B4tel+de+Boisgelin%22+aix&hl=en&sa=X&ei=YE-7Uoy0OPDe7AbUxoH4Dg&ved=0CIMBEOgBMAk4Cg]</ref>

1964年，该建筑列为[[法国历史遗迹|法国历史遗迹]]。

